---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base>
  <div class="intro">
    <h1>Lucas Beillo</h1>
    <p class="muted mono" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">Data analyst &amp; data engineer · A Coruña, Spain</p>

    <p>
      I build and analyze data systems — pipelines, warehouses, and the dashboards and models that sit on top
      of them. Day to day that's Python, SQL, dbt, and DuckDB.
    </p>
    <p>
      A background in GIS and environmental analysis is a plus, not the point: spatial and sensor data don't
      scare me, but the work is the data stack.
    </p>
    <p>
      On the side I build Life Tracker, a personal data warehouse that pulls my own data from five sources
      into a single analytical model — an excuse to run a full pipeline end to end.
    </p>
    <p>
      Outside work, I run. More on that soon.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Recent projects</h2>
    <div class="card-list">
      <div class="card" style="display: block;">
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 1rem;">
          <span class="card-title">Life Tracker <span class="mono muted">(healthkit)</span></span>
          <span class="card-meta">in development</span>
        </div>
        <span class="card-desc">
          Personal data warehouse aggregating five sources into one analytical model.
          Pipeline: Python → DuckDB → dbt → Flask API → React dashboard.
        </span>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag">Python</span>
          <span class="tag">DuckDB</span>
          <span class="tag">dbt</span>
          <span class="tag">Flask</span>
          <span class="tag">React</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card" style="display: block;">
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 1rem;">
          <span class="card-title">Recolle</span>
          <span class="card-meta">2025–</span>
        </div>
        <span class="card-desc">Civic-tech platform turning urban waste and environmental reports into structured, queryable data for Galician cities.</span>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag">Python</span>
          <span class="tag">SQL</span>
          <span class="tag">data pipeline</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Stack</h2>
    <p class="mono muted">SQL · Python · DuckDB · dbt · Flask · React · Power BI · QGIS · Git</p>
  </div>
</Base>
